name: Meexo
overview:
Meexo is a fun, safe and private way to meet new people.

What’s your type? Let Meexo figure it out. The more you use the app, the more it learns what kind of people you’re into…Without the burden of extensive personality tests. Start browsing through photos of real people immediately. Spend more time getting to know people and less time answering questions.

Meexo is private. On Meexo, you will only see profiles of people you don’t already know. So no need to worry about running into your ex, your classmates or your co-workers as long as you are friends with them on Facebook.

Meexo is safe. Meexo does not share your exact location with strangers. Only your city is disclosed. Also, you don’t have to reveal your phone number when texting others.

Meexo is real. You can only create one profile per device. Gone the days when people could create many fake accounts and get away with it!

Meexo is available for free in the iPhone App Store.
